  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001447.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Thirty-five years after Umma had been divided up , Lugal-ana-tum , governor of Umma , built the E-gidru in Umma . He drove in its foundation pegs , and within it he put its divine powers in good order ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001447.14",
      "line_range": "14",
      "translation": "(14) At that time Si’um was the king of Gutium ."
    }
  ],
